{
  "texts": [
    "By calculating the Intraclass Correlation Coefficient (ICC) for the difference scores between the pre-and post-intervention nominal data, we obtained an ICC value of 0.76, indicating good agreement between the raters.",
    "Tables 4 and 5 examined the existence of significant differences between the two summaries of a student, namely \"Pre\" and \"Post.\"",
    "The objective was to assess whether the measured variable demonstrated noticeable variations following a specific intervention with AI tutor bot.",
    "Specifically, in comparison of \"Pre\" and \"Post\" sample groups, the test revealed: t = -9.220, df = 50, p < 0.05, with a mean value for the \"Pre\" group of 4.57 and for the \"Post\" group of 6.24.",
    "This test result thus indicates a quite sharp variation in the measured variable after intervention."
  ]
}